---
---
<section id="hero" class="hero">
  <div class="container hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-badge reveal">
      <span class="dot"></span>
      <span>Made with Claude IA · Entretien Individuel 2026</span>
    </div>

    <h1 class="reveal">
      Quentin <span class="gradient-text">Charton</span>
      <br/><span class="hero-subtitle">Rétrospective d'une année au cœur des pôles</span>
    </h1>

    <div class="stripes-deco reveal" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <p class="hero-lead reveal">
      J'ai pris le pli de l'IA assez rapidement — je joue avec l'IA depuis 2022.
      Heureux d'avoir rejoint le pôle IA l'année dernière, j'ai passé l'année à concevoir
      des outils pour les différents pôles, à imaginer des solutions sur-mesure pour nos
      clients, et à entretenir nos relations partenaires.
    </p>

    <div class="hero-stats reveal">
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-value gradient-text">2022</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Découverte de l'IA</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-value gradient-text">5</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Pôles servis</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-value gradient-text">5</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Partenaires</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-value gradient-text">∞</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Problèmes résolus</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-cta reveal">
      <a href="#hub" class="btn-primary">Voir mes projets par pôle</a>
      <a href="#bilan" class="btn-secondary">Aller au bilan</a>
    </div>

    <div class="scroll-hint reveal">
      <span>Scroll</span>
      <div class="scroll-line"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 80px 0 60px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .hero-inner {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 900px;
  }

  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 8px 18px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--surface-strong);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text-1);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  .hero-badge .dot {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--mint-deep);
    box-shadow: 0 0 12px var(--mint-deep);
    animation: pulse 2s infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0.4; }
  }

  .stripes-deco {
    width: 140px;
    height: 6px;
    margin: 24px auto 0;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: repeating-linear-gradient(
      90deg,
      var(--mint) 0 14px,
      var(--rose) 14px 22px,
      var(--sky) 22px 32px,
      var(--butter) 32px 38px,
      var(--lavender) 38px 52px
    );
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 16px;
    font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2.5vw, 1.8rem);
    color: var(--text-2);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .hero-lead {
    margin: 32px auto 0;
    max-width: 680px;
    color: var(--text-1);
    font-size: 1.15rem;
  }

  .hero-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    margin: 56px 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .hero-stats { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }

  .stat {
    padding: 24px 12px;
    background: var(--surface-strong);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
    transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
  }

  .stat:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 18px 50px -15px rgba(58, 70, 120, 0.2);
  }

  .stat-value {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.4rem);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-2);
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .hero-cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-primary, .btn-secondary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 14px 28px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--lavender-deep), var(--mint-deep));
    color: white;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px -8px rgba(157, 127, 209, 0.5);
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 16px 40px -8px rgba(157, 127, 209, 0.65);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: var(--surface-strong);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    color: var(--text-0);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: white;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .scroll-hint {
    margin-top: 80px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    color: var(--text-3);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  }

  .scroll-line {
    width: 1px;
    height: 40px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--lavender-deep), transparent);
    animation: float 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
</style>
